	filled blocks as an EOF indicator. Issue a warning if
	a single one is encountered.
	* src/system.c (sys_stat_nanoseconds): New function
	* src/tar.h (tar_stat_info.atime_nsec,mtime_nsec,ctime_nsec): New
	members.
